casebody.data:
Office of Disciplinary Counsel v. DiCarlantonio.

[Cite as Disciplinary Counsel v. DiCarlantonio (1994), 68 Ohio St.3d 479.]

*480(No. 93-1737 Submitted January 4, 1994 Decided March 23, 1994.) *481Geoffrey Stem, Disciplinary Counsel, and Karen B. Hull, Assistant Disciplinary Counsel, for relator. Anthony R. DiCarlantonio, pro se. Per Curiam.

We concur in the findings and recommendation of the board. Anthony R. DiCarlantonio is hereby permanently disbarred. Costs taxed to respondent.

Judgment accordingly.

Moyer, C.J., A.W. Sweeney, Douglas, Wright, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney and Pfeifer, JJ., concur.'
